quizzes.textContent:
[h1]Nested Hashes[/h1]

Hashes can also be nested.[code format="rb" codeId="1033"]cars = {
  bmw: { year:2016, color:"red"},
  mercedes: { year:2012, color:"black"},
  porsche: { year:2014, color:"white"}
}

puts cars[:bmw][:color]
# outputs "red"[/code]
[note]Hashes and arrays can have any level of nesting, but keep in mind that hashes and arrays with more than three dimensions are harder to manage.[/note]
